    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>技术问题或BUG反馈 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎加入企鹅群解决 975109596</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Rolling in the Maze》中，玩家化身一个小球破解重重迷宫。为了走到终点，玩家需要按照每关不同的关卡机制对应破解。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899400/extras/7abc05aa07e8fa92a02ae8a573a2abc1.poster.avif?t=1771839572\" width=480 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899400/extras/7abc05aa07e8fa92a02ae8a573a2abc1.webm?t=1771839572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899400/extras/7abc05aa07e8fa92a02ae8a573a2abc1.mp4?t=1771839572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款休闲类小球迷宫游戏，游戏目前有10个关卡，每关的机制各不相同，按键盘上的“A”和“D”控制迷宫的旋转，迷宫中的小球会随重力移动， <br>每关有三颗星星，让我们破解迷宫走到终点吧。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899400/extras/4017a5e96b778eb2725779f1b1d16e52.poster.avif?t=1771839572\" width=480 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899400/extras/4017a5e96b778eb2725779f1b1d16e52.webm?t=1771839572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899400/extras/4017a5e96b778eb2725779f1b1d16e52.mp4?t=1771839572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >休闲迷宫游戏</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整版10个大关卡49个小关卡</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的旋转控制小球机制</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >愉快的音乐氛围 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899400/extras/1dc685ebeb212829f168058b3a5c34e8.poster.avif?t=1771839572\" width=480 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899400/extras/1dc685ebeb212829f168058b3a5c34e8.webm?t=1771839572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899400/extras/1dc685ebeb212829f168058b3a5c34e8.mp4?t=1771839572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在选关界面同时按下键盘字母区域上方的“2”和“5”即可暂时解锁关卡。</p>",
